trans-unit.source: The StripLinesCollection class represents a collection of <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.StripLine> objects, and is implemented as the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis.StripLines%2A> property of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis> class.
trans-unit.target: StripLinesCollection 클래스 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.StripLine>개체</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.StripLine> 및 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis.StripLines%2A> <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis>클래스</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis> 의 속성</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis.StripLines%2A> 으로 구현 되는 컬렉션을 나타냅니다.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.StripLine> objects can be appended, inserted or removed from the collection at both design time and run time.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.StripLine>개체는 추가, 삽입 또는 디자인 타임 및 런타임 모두에서 컬렉션에서 제거할 수 있습니다.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.StripLine>

trans-unit.source: **Note** Strip lines can be displayed once or repeatedly for a set interval.
trans-unit.target: **참고** 줄무늬 선을 간격 설정에 대 한에 한 번 또는 반복적으로 표시 됩니다.
